data.description:
Assumable VA loan at 2.675%! Contact me for more info! Offers a 5th bedroom (non-conforming) with en suite bathroom!

Cayhill beauty with so much to offer! The curb appeal will welcome you in to the main level - where you will find a formal dining room, breakfast area, and beautiful cabinetry and countertops in the kitchen. Walk straight out to the fenced backyard with extended deck. Master suite also on the main level that connects to the laundry room, along with a half bath for guests! 3 bedrooms and full bathroom on the 2nd level with two of the bedrooms having their own separate play or storage spaces! Downstairs you will find a finished basement with potential for a 5th bedroom(no egress), guest suite or office space. Basement also offers a full bathroom, wet bar with wine cooler, and a huge storage space with tons of shelving! You don't want to miss this one!
